{"tid":2010228,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社區組織協會：無家者疫情下失業　促政府設失業援助金","createTime":"2020-05-10T09:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T09:59:59.000Z","uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d38087030262b2c217410eb0f2e968e4d8bba3f","tid":2010228,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"29分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390524&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390524%26home%3D1&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQg0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=b7258c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390524%26home%3D1&h=b02e2176\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390524&amp;home=1</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】社區組織協會的調查顯示，很多無家者在疫情下失業，促請政府設收容中心，及發放失業援助金。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會問卷訪問104名無家者，六成四人今年才成為無家者，102人在疫情前都有工作，平均月入一萬二千元，疫情以來96人失業，要靠積蓄及借貸，甚至拾荒維生，他們一半人是被解僱，其餘被放無薪假，或失去原先的散工，主要從事飲食、運輸、清潔及地盤，而有工作的受訪者，平均收入跌至不足五千元，九成三受訪者未能受惠於抗疫基金。<br />\n<br />\n多數人希望政府增設失業援助金，每月補貼最少七千元，及向無家者開放收容中心。"},{"pid":"1c47924e01ae68395bfdfde9b2a82416279f9994","tid":2010228,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"個政府點會幫我呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a5aefe02e29a1c5b9eaf1c0362f4c5bfd88100","tid":2010228,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c47924e01ae68395bfdfde9b2a82416279f9994","tid":2010228,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"個政府點會幫我呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7166635ae97b1ea36e6c2f458